messages.message:
Hi Team,
We just changed the flake8 pre-commit check (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/30192) to enforce no unused imports in python.
If there are places where you need to import a module without using it, you can add `# noqa: F401` . Learn more about noqa here (https://flake8.pycqa.org/en/3.0.2/user/ignoring-errors.html#in-line-ignoring-errors)
